comments: RUI - The scores are based on the assumption between "hard" and "workload".
paraphrases: Do you know whether EECS 280 is hard ?
For EECS 280 , is it always hard ?
Will EECS 280 be a challenging course ?
Would EECS 280 be considered harder than most ?
Would you rate EECS 280 as hard ?
Would you say that EECS 280 is hard ?
sql: SELECT PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.WORKLOAD FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 280 AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID ;
sql-with-vars: SELECT PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.WORKLOAD FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "department0" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = number0 AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID ;
